# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

_SCUBA2_HELLO_ - Mandatory introductory primitive

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 _SCUBA2_HELLO_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive should be called at the start of all SCUBA-2 DR recipes.
It makes sure that history recording is enabled.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

Probably not required for QuickLook mode.

=head1 ALGORITHMS

Uses KAPPA HISSET.

